{
  "stem": "20710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After dinner, we used to-- instead of going to this house, you know, where they-- where they housed the woman, we slept in the field, so he can--",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There weren't that time too many guards at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was not-- this was not a camp that was surrounded with-- with wire.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was sort of like a open field.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came that time and he took me out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just-- I guess but a week after, they came in and they liquidated the-- the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- I was in the forest with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who liquidated the camp?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] So, a lot of peoples runs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they-- they escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whichever way where they were, where they worked, that they could, you know, run away, they-- they run away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But most of them, they were just taken on-- on the-- on trucks and this-- took to-- to-- to the trains, where-- I don't even know where they took them afterwards.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- a lot of the times I go to-- here to the holocaust, you know, that they have here in Mount Sinai, I don't even know which way, because there's so many places where they took-- I don't even know where they took my parents.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, he took me to the-- and I was there from-- they liquidated, I think, in-- during summer, in July, June, July.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we spent in there, [SIGHS] in the forest, a whole summer and a whole winter-- I mean, the rest of the summer and the whole winter.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you describe how you lived while you were there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How we lived in the beginning was very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, see, the-- the forest was-- again, we going back to Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The forest was-- Hanaczow was surrounded with this forest.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
